# API Client Conventions

- Use the shared `api` instance from `src/api/client.js` instead of creating new axios clients.
- Keep the base URL sourced from `VITE_API_URL` with a safe local default.
- Always set `withCredentials: true` to send cookies with cross-origin requests (required for Cloudflare Access authentication).
- Add auth headers via the request interceptor rather than per-call duplication.
- Log and rethrow errors in the response interceptor; avoid silent failures.
